o other asia pacific countries by setting up top solvent vietnam limited liability company in ho chi minh city to distribute solvents and chemicals which is imported from thailand and others under the direction of its professional teams with more than  years of experience in the production and sale of solvents and chemicals as well as the business potential of its affiliation with thai oil and ptt public company limited top solvent commands a diverse product distribution capability the company has also demonstrated a logistical readiness to deliver products in assorted containers—drums iso tanks and bulk containers—by truck vessel and pipeline top solvent is committed to sustainable growth in all its business operations and is poised to develop new products and services to meet customers’ demand it is also ready to grow its customer base in thailand vietnam and other countries in the region and to realize its business goals of stakeholder satisfaction environmental protection and social balance download  about us top solvent coltd  energy complex building a th floor vibhavadi rangsit road chatuchak bangkok  thailandtel             fax    follow us ampampampampampamplta hrefhttpwwwhistatscom targetblankampampampampampampgt ampampampampampampltimg srchttpshistatscomstatsgifampampampampampampamp altinvisible hit counter borderampampampampampampgtampampampampampampltaampampampampampampgt whos online we have  guests and no members online copyright   top solvent coltd   ，  ， ： 、  （：ptt public company limited  ：บริษัท ปตท จำกัด），pttปตท ，，。 、、、，，。 ，；。   （）   “httpszhwikipediaorgwindexphptitleoldid” ：：                         irc  pdf    deutschenglishفارسیfrançaisbahasa indonesiaportuguêsрусскийไทย    。   ，。（） wikipedia®；™。 c、、。     cookie    ，  ， ： 、  （：ptt public company limited  ：บริษัท ปตท จำกัด），pttปตท ，，。 、、、，，。 ，；。   （）   “httpszhwikipediaorgwindexphptitleoldid” ：：                         irc  pdf    deutschenglishفارسیfrançaisbahasa indonesiaportuguêsрусскийไทย    。